Professional Statement:
I am a detail-oriented and solution-driven technologist passionate about building secure and scalable applications. With strong programming skills in technologies like React JS, Node.js, and MongoDB, I bring a problem-solving mindset and a commitment to ethical technology use. I aim to contribute to innovative projects that prioritize sustainability, user privacy, and long-term impact. Whether at a tech startup, in government service, or with a socially responsible organization, I strive to use my skills to design systems that are not only efficient but also aligned with the greater good.
